      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the reassurance. i was worried i might need to go back to the clinic but that sounds way easier. just to be sure, how often should i be doing the warm compress and how much of the antiseptic cream should i use? i want to make sure i dont overdo it but also make sure it clears up fast.",
