      "content": "okay sounds good. i think i have some neosporin here. if the redness starts spreading a bit more tomorrow, should i just double up on the cream or maybe add some hydrogen peroxide to the cleaning routine to really kill anything in there? i'd rather just fix it myself if i can so i don't have to pay for another doctor visit.",
